---
name: get_store_inventory_health
description: >
  Sweep the entire Shopify store inventory to classify all SKUs by velocity
  (FAST/STEADY/SLOW/STALE) and flag out-of-stock risk. Returns aggregate
  health score, overstock count, stockout risk count, and top 10 products by
  each class.
---
Use for store-wide inventory health questions, not single-SKU questions.
